OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FIf there was any doubt about it
OL,7,Fbefore, the Wales Debate has proven
OL,8,Fonce and for all how much Wales and,
OL,9,Fin particular, Welsh devolution is
OL,10,Fbeing thrust to the centre of this UK
OL,11,FGeneral Election campaign.
OL,13,FIn itself, that's not new. I remember
OL,14,F2015 when David Cameron repeated his
OL,15,Fline that Offa's Dyke had become "the
OL,16,Fline between life and death,"
OL,17,Fhighlighting what he said were
OL,18,FLabour's failures in running the
OL,19,Fhealth service on this side of the
OL,20,Fborder.
