OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FBut that was nothing compared to the
OL,7,Fway that in 2024, Conservatives are
OL,8,Frepeatedly highlighting Labour's
OL,9,Frecord here in Wales, gleefully
OL,10,Fquoting Keir Starmer saying two years
OL,11,Fago that he saw Welsh Labour as a
OL,12,F"blueprint" for a UK Government.
OL,14,FIt's not just the Conservatives doing
OL,15,Fit either. Plaid Cymru, the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats and now Reform UK are all
OL,17,Ftaking a similar approach.
