OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FIn the debate, David TC Davies,
OL,7,Frepeatedly said that the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment gets #1.20 for every #1
OL,9,Fspent on the health service in
OL,10,FEngland, making the point that
OL,11,Fministers in Cardiff chose not to
OL,12,Fwaste that money on other projects.
OL,14,FIt's certainly true that there are
OL,15,Frules in place to ensure that when
OL,16,Fmoney is spent on services in England
OL,17,Fthat are devolved, it triggers funding
OL,18,Ffor Wales of at least 115%.
