OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FDevolution means there's no obligation
OL,7,Fon the Welsh Government to spend the
OL,8,Fmoney on the same priorities. It makes
OL,9,Fits own political choices, political
OL,10,Fchoices that can and are being
OL,11,Fcriticised by opponents within and
OL,12,Foutside Wales.
OL,14,FWelsh Labour also argues that the
OL,15,FConservative UK Government has
OL,16,Fgradually eroded the overall budget it
OL,17,Fcould expect to receive for specific
OL,18,Fservices, leaving its ministers to
OL,19,Fmake up the shortfalls from parts of
OL,20,Fthe budget it would rather ring fence.
