OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Liz Saville Roberts also
OL,7,Fcriticised Labour's record in Wales
OL,8,Fduring the debate. She said that "when
OL,9,Fit comes to health ... I greatly fear
OL,10,Fthe model that is set by Labour here"
OL,11,Fand that it is "intolerable" that "19%
OL,12,Fof the Welsh population" is waiting
OL,13,Ffor treatment here.
OL,15,FShe set out her party's pledge to
OL,16,Frecruit 500 new GPs and to pay people
OL,17,Fworking in the care system more in
OL,18,Forder to increase capacity there.
