OL,6,FIf you remember, Vaughan Gething
OL,7,Fpledged in his leadership campaign
OL,8,Fthat the Welsh NHS won't be privatised.
OL,10,FThere's a big argument about what
OL,11,Fprivatisation means, but here in Wales
OL,12,Fthere has long been a reluctance to
OL,13,Fuse the private sector - something
OL,14,Fraised by David Davies in the debate.
