OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FLabour's Shadow Health Secretary Wes
OL,7,FStreeting has faced controversy by
OL,8,Fopenly talking about using the private
OL,9,Fsector to help cut waiting times in
OL,10,FEngland, saying that not to do so
OL,11,Fwould be a "betrayal" of working-class
OL,12,Fpeople by "middle-class lefties."
OL,14,FIn the debate, Jo Stevens hailed the
OL,15,Fprospect of two Labour governments
OL,16,Fworking together, saying that the last
OL,17,Ftime that happened the NHS had the
OL,18,F"highest satisfaction levels".
