OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FBut the last time there were two
OL,7,Fgovernments, senior Welsh Labour
OL,8,Ffigures felt the need to distance
OL,9,Fthemselves from the market-oriented,
OL,10,Fprivate-public reforms of the Blair
OL,11,Fand Brown governments - a distancing
OL,12,Fsummed up with the phrase "clear red
OL,13,Fwater" coined by Mark Drakeford, used
OL,14,Fby Rhodri Morgan and continued by
OL,15,FCarwyn Jones.
