OL,3,CWales Debate: Devolution thrust to
OL,4,Ccentre of UK election campaigns
OL,6,FAfter July 4, if the polls are right,
OL,7,Fthere could be a large bloc of newly-
OL,8,Fempowered Welsh Labour MPs assertively
OL,9,Fpromoting the ideas of a highly-
OL,10,Fenergised Starmer government with a
OL,11,Fsuper-majority in the UK Parliament.
OL,12,FAnd, if what Wes Streeting has said
OL,13,Fcomes about, that could mean a very
OL,14,Fdifferent approach to running the
OL,15,Fhealth service than that which has
OL,16,Fbeen followed by Labour in Cardiff Bay.
